title: 820 3115 missing PP5V_S3
message: I got it working now, this machine has an EFI swap done on it at some point in the past. The solder joints looked so/so, I pulled the chip and resoldered it. The machine boots now. Thanks John

title: 820 3115 missing PP5V_S3
message:
Quarter fan spin means PP5V_S3 is pulsing at least.
The fan requires 5V_S0 to spin.
So your board tries to enter S0 even...

Look if all big coils pulse.
ALL_SYS_PWRGD pulsing too?

I hope PPBUS_G3H and 3V3_S5 are stable; you didn't mention them.

title: 820 3115 missing PP5V_S3
message: 2info, I got it solved, it was a poorly soldered SPI ROM, done by some one previously. Thank you
